   <description><![CDATA[Call Me Back module developed by itfirmaet.dk ApS. Simple Call Me Back form. Gives the end user the possibility to request a phone call. The user types name and phone number and submits the form. When the form is submitted an email is send to the address configured in the module. Visit itfirmaet.dk for more professional Joomla extensions]]>
   </description>
   <files>
      <filename>mod_itf_call_me_back.xml</filename>
      <filename module="mod_itf_call_me_back">mod_itf_call_me_back.php</filename>
      <filename>helper.php</filename>
